### 1. Sign Up
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login (Get Token)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Add a Book (Requires Token)
# Copy the token from the login response and replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
POST http://localhost:8080/books/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "The Great Gatsby",
  "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
  "genre": "Classic"
}

### 4. Search Books (Requires Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?title=Gatsby
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
